N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 170.11 - Advertisements

State Regulations

All media advertisements placed by an individual or
business licensed under this article, other than a proprietary security guard
company, shall state, "Licensed by the New York State Department of

State."
